<p><strong>Summary: </strong>
Here I draw two entries from my #journal; annotating some thoughts as well as how I&rsquo;ve expanded my #writing process over the last two months.  There&rsquo;s a #poem in here as well.
</p>
        <p>On <time datetime="2024-11-12" title="2024-11-12">Tuesday the 12th of November, 2024</time>, I started what I hoped to be a new habit.
That is writing a personal daily journal.  Over the weeks, I expanded my
aspirations to include a daily check list of activities I wanted to do.</p>
<p>I‚Äôve also used these journals to spin-off blog posts; such as this one.  In
other words, my daily journal is growing a virtuous cycle in my creative
process.</p>
